snippet.title: Red Colony - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Red Colony is a 2D Ecchi Horror Game filled with Drama, mystery, Zombies and gore. Help Maria find her daughter, revenge her cheating Husband and find out what happen to her beloved Colony.

Read more over at: https://www.runiccodes.com/
